info:doi/10.2337%2Fdc06-0922&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/17327321&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcare.diabetesjournals.org%2Fcgi%2Fcontent%2Fabstract%2F30%2F3%2F561&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Sugar"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> See table 6, page 56 of the WHO Technical Report Series 916, <i>Diet, Nutrition and the Prevention of Chronic Diseases</i>: online at <a href="http://www.fao.org/docrep/005/AC911E/ac911e07.htm#bm07.1.3" class="external free" title="http://www.fao.org/docrep/005/AC911E/ac911e07.htm#bm07.1.3" rel="nofollow">http://www.fao.org/docrep/005/AC911E/ac911e07.htm#bm07.1.3</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.vegfamily.com/articles/sugar.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.vegfamily.com/articles/sugar.htm" rel="nofollow">The Great Sugar Debate: Is it Vegan?</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-VegetarianJournal-15">^ <a href="#cite_ref-VegetarianJournal_15-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-VegetarianJournal_15-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFYacoubou.2C_MS2007">Yacoubou, MS, Jeanne (2007). "<a href="https://www.vrg.org/journal/vj2007issue4/vj2007issue4.pdf" class="external text" title="https://www.vrg.org/journal/vj2007issue4/vj2007issue4.pdf" rel="nofollow">Is Your Sugar Vegan? An Update on Sugar Processing Practices</a>" (PDF). <i>Vegetarian Journal</i> (Baltimore, MD: The Vegetarian Resource Group) <b>26</b> (4): 16–20<span class="printonly">. <a href="https://www.vrg.org/journal/vj2007issue4/vj2007issue4.pdf" class="external free" title="https://www.vrg.org/journal/vj2007issue4/vj2007issue4.pdf" rel="nofollow">https://www.vrg.org/journal/vj2007issue4/vj2007issue4.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-04-04</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Is+Your+Sugar+Vegan%3F+An+Update+on+Sugar+Processing+Practices&amp;rft.jtitle=Vegetarian+Journal&amp;rft.aulast=Yacoubou%2C+MS&amp;rft.aufirst=Jeanne&amp;rft.au=Yacoubou%2C+MS%2C+Jeanne&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.volume=26&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=16%E2%80%9320&amp;rft.place=Baltimore%2C+MD&amp;rft.pub=The+Vegetarian+Resource+Group&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vrg.org%2Fjournal%2Fvj2007issue4%2Fvj2007issue4.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Sugar"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
